## Summary
Nami is a platform for in-app purchases and subscriptions that integrates with Amplitude to send subscription-related events, requiring a paid Nami plan and matching user identifiers across both platforms for proper data merging. The integration enables monetization optimization, targeted conversion campaigns, and real-time revenue analytics.

